<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>CTE | BITS Goa</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="icon" href="https://bpgc-cte.org/logo.png" type="image/png">
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-900 text-white font-sans">

    <header class="sticky top-0 bg-gray-900/80 backdrop-blur border-b border-gray-700">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-lg">
                <img src="https://bpgc-cte.org/logo.png" alt="CTE Logo" class="w-8 h-8">
                <span>CTE | BITS Goa</span>
            </div>

            <div>
                <a href="/auth/google" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 
          hover:from-blue-600 hover:via-purple-600 hover:to-pink-600 
          text-white font-semibold shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
                    Login
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="text-center py-24 px-6">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
            Fostering Technical Culture Since 2012
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
            We conduct courses, workshops, host technical competitions, offer financial assistance to technical clubs
            and projects, and organise academic help sessions.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
            <a href="#courses" class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-black font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg">
                Find Courses
            </a>
            <a href="#initiatives" class="border border-gray-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-800">
                What We Do
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="initiatives" class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
        <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-8 flex-wrap gap-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">What we do</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Center for Technical Education at BITS Pilani, Goa Campus</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">AAP (Academic Assistance Programme)</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">Helping students grasp concepts, tackle problems, and excel with guidance
                    from mentors.</p>
                <a href="#aap" class="text-green-400 hover:underline">Learn more</a>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Courses</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">Wide-ranging courses from music theory to robotics, led by skilled
                    instructors.</p>
                <a href="#courses" class="text-green-400 hover:underline">Browse courses</a>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Tech Weekend</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">Hackathons and competitions across domains—from finance to aerospace.</p>
                <a href="#techweekend" class="text-green-400 hover:underline">See events</a>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Project Fundings</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">We fund up to 10 projects with support up to Rs 40,000.</p>
                <a href="#funding" class="text-green-400 hover:underline">Apply for funding</a>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">TechForums</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">An online space with tags, discussions, moderators, and timed events.</p>
                <a href="#forums" class="text-green-400 hover:underline">Join the forums</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Why collaborate with us?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300">
            CTE is the premier technical organisation of BITS Goa. We collaborate widely, run acclaimed events, and
            consistently see strong participation.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Impact</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold">3000+</div>
                <div class="text-gray-400">Students Taught</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold">40+</div>
                <div class="text-gray-400">Projects Funded</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold">250K+</div>
                <div class="text-gray-400">Cash Prizes Rewarded</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold">110+</div>
                <div class="text-gray-400">Pizzas Ordered</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
        <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-6 flex-wrap gap-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Our Team</h2>
            <a href="#meet-team" class="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-600 rounded hover:bg-gray-800">Meet the Team</a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400">With a technical department this big come big responsibilities—and we’re used to
            handling them.</p>
    </section>

    <footer class="border-t border-gray-700 py-6 text-center text-gray-400">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <img src="https://bpgc-cte.org/logo.png" alt="CTE Logo" class="w-6 h-6">
            <span>© CTE BPGC 2025</span>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>

</html>